data.description: Meticulously maintained 5 bed, 4 bath with study, highly desired Grayson floor plan is perfect for entertaining. Spacious gourmet kitchen features a gas cooktop with vented decorative hood and oversized island, open to the great room with cozy gas fireplace. This one level plan offers an isolated owners' suite with glam bath, separate vanities and spacious closet. Secondary bedrooms are en-suites, easily accessible. Beautifully upgraded trim, trey ceilings, formal dining with craftsman wainscoting and hardwood flooring through main living areas.  3 car side-entry garage with long & extra wide driveway. Close to Shopping, Redstone Arsenal and Madison City Schools.
